#

Slow-Cooked BBQ Beef Brisket

$25
400 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

Slow-CookedBBQComfort Food

Description

Tender, smoky, and flavorful brisket, perfect for any gathering.

Ingredients

  • Beef Brisket: 3 pounds
  • BBQ Sauce: 1 cup
  • Onion: 1 large, sliced
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Beef Broth: 2 cups
  • Brown Sugar: 2 tablespoons
  • Paprika: 1 tablespoon
  • Salt: 1 teaspoon
  • Black Pepper: 1 teaspoon
  • Cayenne Pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
